    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048660/extras/a67223fa8fb3589664d8eb387a6700fd.avif?t=1746774113\" width=625 height=300 /></span>PS：为满足所有玩家获取需求，此次QQ群将不定期进行清理，如有需要可重复添加。  感谢理解~ <br><strong>对于无法加入QQ群的玩家们可通过游戏商店页面—社区中心加入steam讨论组</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048660/extras/7c2a1272ce7bc77e444f96041dab0e34.avif?t=1746774113\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048660/extras_big/7c2a1272ce7bc77e444f96041dab0e34.avif?t=1746774113 width=800 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>已经购买过勾八公主狂想曲的玩家无需购买公主：东方与远征</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048660/extras/f28fd27e1d39fb1d3d47bc6cf5ca4761.avif?t=1746774113\" width=624 height=300 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048660/extras/d7737a40cf7105afdc8be2061b119b9f.avif?t=1746774113\" width=624 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048660/extras/d8a77e070b130674df017e640e92982d.avif?t=1746774113\" width=590 height=190 /></span>     古代风流传我们获得了广大玩家的喜爱，同时也收到了大家的反馈，我们积极解决整改团队。在延续古代风流转剧情的基础上，开发出了游戏续作《公主：东方与远征》游戏采用肉鸽玩法操作主角征战四方，开启与不同国度美少女的奇妙之旅。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    在游戏开发制作上我们组建了更为专业的游戏团队，摒弃AI使用纯手绘画法以及大量的剧情文本等，带给广大玩家身临其境的感觉。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    最后，感谢您对《公主：东方与远征》制作的支持。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048660/extras/a18368f102c47d2422af8adfcd2a2c48.avif?t=1746774113\" width=590 height=190 /></span>《公主：东方与远征》是一款包含“美少女+Roguelike+即时战略”的游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  作为皇帝钦命的远征将军，你需要通过自己的智慧和胆识征战未知的国度扩张领土 ，揭穿隐藏在黑暗深处的阴谋。期间你还会邂逅各式各样不同风情的美少女，助力你的征战之路</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048660/extras/48437a4021b28873493b931339efa846.avif?t=1746774113\" width=590 height=190 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048660/extras/b4bbbfa9b9e9dc8bbff21419b9d54f40.avif?t=1746774113\" width=624 height=350 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048660/extras/a6049f90bfe3b4a67e071adb9e39cce9.avif?t=1746774113\" width=624 height=300 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048660/extras/80a46deb2252f4f622286542c1c96e80.avif?t=1746774113\" width=624 height=300 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048660/extras/65be138ec0a8ef6992444c5d5ffb3e63.avif?t=1746774113\" width=624 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048660/extras/9460d894f9e930e5ed496d0bdc2955bf.avif?t=1746774113\" width=590 height=190 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048660/extras/3926644e57510e93431dd381b683ff6c.avif?t=1746774113\" width=728 height=768 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048660/extras/b910720815c4162deae082376c3b9e6d.avif?t=1746774113\" width=728 height=1046 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048660/extras/cd14ea3da1ab2d54dffd0d8729d3e2f8.avif?t=1746774113\" width=590 height=190 /></span><strong>大妖手绘稿</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048660/extras/cde60faf686dda852754d376392f5d8e.avif?t=1746774113\" width=728 height=1046 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>宦官手绘稿</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048660/extras/8aa683120d06d3ff2be47ceb2aadaae0.avif?t=1746774113\" width=728 height=1046 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>女主Q版手绘稿</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048660/extras/961ef66635cd0bdc84ccc6bf902ee252.avif?t=1746774113\" width=728 height=1046 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>女主立绘手绘稿示例</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048660/extras/6d53eafe30d12e0eb7f8d20d21b80aec.avif?t=1746774113\" width=370 height=498 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048660/extras/4e66a5826e00cbb6cf40ed6ad9227c33.avif?t=1746774113\" width=590 height=190 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets